---
---
<section class="home-section fade-in" id="home-favorites">
  <div class="section-head section-head-row">
    <div>
      <p class="section-kicker">我的收藏</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">本地收藏的工具</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">保存在本浏览器，无需登录；可导出备份或导入到其他设备</p>
    </div>
    <div class="favorites-actions">
      <button type="button" class="cta-btn cta-btn-outline" id="favorites-export" data-track="favorite_export">导出 JSON</button>
      <label class="cta-btn cta-btn-outline favorites-import-label">
        导入
        <input type="file" id="favorites-import" accept="application/json,.json" hidden />
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="learning-continue" id="learning-continue" hidden>
    <p class="recommend-card-lead">继续学习</p>
    <ul class="learning-continue-list" id="learning-continue-list"></ul>
  </div>
  <p class="favorites-empty" id="favorites-empty">还没有收藏。浏览热门工具，点 ☆ 即可加入学习清单。</p>
  <ul class="favorites-list" id="favorites-list"></ul>
</section>
